data.description: Come walkthrough this Beautiful, fully rehabbed 5 bdr/3bth home located near the center of sought after Wheeling IL. Very nice sized 5 bedrooms with 3 stylish bathrooms and kitchen to compliment the easygoing flow to the living room, dining room, and sun room that this house offers. Master bedroom on second level has its own bathroom and walk in closet. Closets in all rooms, and storage throughout the house. Spacious enough to enjoy time together, as well as delegate privacy when needed. Step outside to enjoy the huge corner lot full of opportunities for projects and entertainment amenities. With renovation's done throughout 2021 to early 2022, this home offers newer plumbing, newer electricity power at 200+ amps, 2 furnaces with central air. 2 car garage with a driveway that can fit 8+cars is perfect for hosting events with friends and family. 6 min drive to local shopping center, 4min away from Wheeling Park district with a huge park to walk/run along a trail. Family indoor/outdoor aquatics center nearby. Plenty of dining and movie theatre/entertainment options nearby. All buyer's have to do is move in with their vision of making this house the perfect home!
